title: Happy NFL New Year! Earl Thomas signs, more OBJ fallout (Football 3/14)
description:
Will Brinson, Sean Wagner, John Breech and Ryan Wilson break down the latest news and notes from free agency including more fallout from the Odell Beckham trade, the Ravens making moves, the Jaguars releasing Blake Bortles, Teddy Bridgewater's status with the Dolphins and much more.
